data.description: Beautiful Mediterranean Home in the Community of Foxfire Ranch sits on a generous 6970sf Lot! This 2976sf living space home has 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. The Jack and Jill bathroom is accessible by 2 of the bedrooms. Loft upstairs can be used as the 6th bedroom if it meets your Large Family needs. The Main Master bedroom is upstairs featuring double door entrance, bathtub, enclosed glass shower, double sink counter and a large walk-in closet with window! Livingroom leads to the Open-concept Kitchen and Family room where you can enjoy the fireplace. Kitchen features Coriander Countertop's, Walk in Pantry and Breakfast bar with sink. Cooling is not an issue with  3 AC units! and a swamp cooler in the Livingroom. Pool out back is ideal for those family parties under the Covered Patio! Fish Pond under tree is included with the Property. This 2 car garage with Vacuum and electric garage door opener (garage door code opener is in garage and outside as well) . Back yard with covered patio. And a front yard with covered front porch. Trees and palmtrees on property.  Surrounded by wood fence. Wood floor and carpet flooring thew out the home. And mostly concrete out back with lanscape by the wood fence. Solar pannels. Central Vacuum.
